{"tid":1756284,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［TKO] [環保北］陳展浚請你公開道歉（全世界入嚟）","createTime":"2019-11-26T03:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T12:17:39.000Z","uid":313692,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"46f2bd6e41b60c3fcbba6c069db587a609f78383","tid":1756284,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"將軍澳人個個都知你既事跡，人格有問題 啲地區工作又做到成pat屎咁<br />\n今年你個943票只不過係你既傳單到呃返黎<br />\n<br />\n自稱民主派唯一候選人&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;同區仲有個前線板仔，黃之鋒都支持佢<br />\n<br />\n聲稱劉小麗支持你&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;老母一早同你割左席<br />\n<br />\n連傳單都可以造假，份人會真？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrZpCvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrZpCvM.png&h=da700852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔只係因為你𠝹何梓聰票而屌鳩你，更因為你打住民主派既旗號做出一啲比保蝗黨更低劣既行為而決定屌鳩你。<br />\n<br />\n當全世界都屌鳩你既時候，你剩係識推卸責任，TKO林奠之名當之無愧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feMZ5VS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeMZ5VS.png&h=2f06a70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]唔該你為自己既失實行為同言論作出道歉！</span>"},{"pid":"dff2c75a77c7becce1cd14ba3557f0a7c6e16e29","tid":1756284,"uid":83609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"1000票都拎唔到就咪獻世啦"},{"pid":"bcebe9dfe69c77b449bc98550cb0dd05eb2ed765","tid":1756284,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"c4fbc6ad4f76170de5363de8da596c0b1a6448b1","tid":1756284,"uid":305579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"佢既惡行<br />\n將軍澳最新既共同敵人&mdash;&mdash;陳展浚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"880ea253a011bd2c296190529c8ea2ac51f5b3dd","tid":1756284,"uid":34244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid